title: Lamborghini driver charged after allegedly mowing down a cyclist on Chapel St in Prahran, Melbourne
description: The cyclist, 46, was crossing Chapel Street at Prahran in Melbourne's inner south when he was allegedly struck about 10.30pm on Saturday night by the Lamborghini.

title: Warren Buffett 'in talks' with White House about investing in banking sector
description: Billionaire Warren Buffett is in talks to invest in the US regional banking sector amidst widespread industry panic not seen since the 2008 financial crisis.

title: Child left on bus in 31C heat by day-care staff at Capalaba Kids Early Learning Centre in Brisbane
description: Capalaba Kids Early Learning Centre in Brisbane's south sent an email to parents after the child, 2, was left unsupervised on the bus as temperatures outside hit 31.1C.

title: Australia could be dragged into war because of its AUKUS nuclear submarine deal, says expert
description: A top defence expert has slammed the AUKUS nuclear submarine deal as amounting to a promise that Australia will follow the US into a war against China.

title: Spring break horror as gunman kills one and injures another in Miami Beach
description: Gunfire erupted in an area of Miami Beach crowded with party goers enjoying booze-filled nights out for spring break, killing one person, wounding another and sending dozens scrambling for safety.

title: Moment doctor is kicked out of Texas Senate after branding gender reassignment surgeons 'pedophiles'
description: Steven Hotze, pictured left, a Houston physician, radio show host and alleged conspiracy theorist, was booted from the Texas Senate on Thursday following a furious anti-trans rant.

title: NSW real estate agents use legal loophole to  get more money for rentals after bidding was banned
description: Landlords have found a sneaky way around a ban on asking for offers above an advertised rental price - they can just wait for prospective tenants to make an offer.

title: Man charged after allegedly attempting to sexually assault woman on Mitchell Street in Bondi
description: A Randwick man has been arrested over an alleged  stalking and attempted sexual assault incident which occurred in the early hours of Friday morning in Sydney's eastern suburbs. He faces five charges..

title: Frozen strawberries sold Costco Trader Joes Aldi recalled HEPATITIS A infections in Washington state

title: SNP chief Paul Murrell forced to quit over revelations the party lied about membership numbers
description: The downfall of Scotland's political power couple followed revelations in The Mail on Sunday that the SNP had lied about its true membership numbers ahead of the leadership race.

title: New app that turns smartphones into dashcams may soon be able to detect SPEEDING

title: Elderly man dies in planned hazard reduction burn-off at Forbes, in the NSW Central West

title: Tara Brown's brother dies less than eight years after his sister was murdered by partner

title: Florida grandmother sues eye drop company after her right eye had to be surgically removed now blind
description: WARNING: GRAPHIC CONTENT CDC says a rare bacterial infection was diagnosed in 68 patients across the US likely caused by preservative-free eyedrops. A woman from Florida is now suing.

title: Gisele Bündchen, 42, steps out for lunch with a male friend after a morning riding along the beach
